    {
      "id": "0mcGcqO0IxMxwc1pGmce_",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -453.16340904628885,
      "y": 3486.987880165393,
      "width": 335.73748779296875,
      "height": 650,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "c-K4riAOyUHThxlNWRNDD"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b20",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1986318157,
      "version": 855,
      "versionNonce": 1652573453,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774716172568,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "FR\n- Ingest images that are taken\nfrom sensors\n- Process them by classifying\nwhat type of image we are dealing\nwith\n- Store the image classification in\nthe DB, so we can look it up later\n- Retrieve the classification\nbased on time rage\n\nOut of scope\n- building the machine learning\nmodel\n\nNFR\n\n- High avalaibility to process the\ndata\n- Durability, make sure to store\nclassification\n- Low Latency, not important here\n- Retentition policy: after 6\nmonth cold storage, 10 years,\nwith different retantion policy\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "FR\n- Ingest images that are taken from sensors\n- Process them by classifying what type of image we are dealing with\n- Store the image classification in the DB, so we can look it up later\n- Retrieve the classification based on time rage\n\nOut of scope\n- building the machine learning model\n\nNFR\n\n- High avalaibility to process the data\n- Durability, make sure to store classification\n- Low Latency, not important here\n- Retentition policy: after 6 month cold storage, 10 years, with different retantion policy\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "zA4mpNhpFJJkP0qsIBKB_",
